
UNIX CB

All commands are preceded by /

a - active users on CB (or /s)
c - change channel
d - send station message
f - change output format
h - change handle
k - boot user
l - toggle channel listing
m - monitor channel one
o - fast log off system
p - send private message
, - send private message to sender of last
/ - send private message to same person
q - log off CB
r - enter private chat mode
t - time status
u - change linefeed char
x - squelch user
y - your status
$ - who is on the system
% - page another user
1 - toggle beeps             2 - toggle linefeeds
3 - toggle ANSI output       4 - toggle station message squelch
5 - toggle Jive translation

